 1995-14401995-08-290,  ,  LAB,  , 
PrecisAppointment of DAVID GOURDEAU, of Beloeil, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Canada Labour Relations Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and order that DAVID GOURDEAU be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective October 2, 1995.

precis:
Appointment of DAVID GOURDEAU, of Beloeil, Quebec, as a full-time member
of the Canada Labour Relations Board to hold office during good behaviour
for a term of five years; and order that DAVID GOURDEAU be deemed to be
employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service
